枝角目是鰓足綱之下的一個目，是一個[[單系群|單系群]]。本目有四個亞目，都是由原來的四個下目升級而成；11個科<ref name=Notothrix /><ref name=Gondwanotrichidae />合共有620個屬，但仍有不少未描述的物種<ref name="Forró">{{cite book |first1=L. |last1=Forró |first2=N. M. |last2=Korovchinsky |first3=A. A. |last3=Kotov |first4=A. |last4=Petrusek |year=2008 |chapter=Global diversity of cladocerans (Cladocera; Crustacea) in freshwater |journal=[[Hydrobiologia|Hydrobiologia]] |volume=595 |issue=1 |pages=177–184 |doi=10.1007/s10750-007-9013-5 |series=Developments in Hydrobiology 198 |title=Freshwater Animal Diversity Assessment |isbn=978-1-4020-8259-7 |editor=Estelle V. Balian, Christian Lévêque, Hendrik Segers & Koen Martens |url=http://decapoda.nhm.org/pdfs/27704/27704.pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |access-date=2014-07-14 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925170035/https://decapoda.nhm.org/pdfs/27704/27704.pdf |dead-url=no }} {{doi|10.1007/978-1-4020-8259-7_19}}</ref>。單單是[[溞科|溞科]]之下的[[水蚤屬|水蚤屬]]，就已經有約150個物種<ref name="Decaestecker"/>。

